c: 12
v: 67
t: "Futhi (ubaba wabo) wathi, “Oh Madodana ami! ningangeni esangweni elilodwa ngenani emasangweni ehlukene futhi angeke nginisize ngalutho kuMvelinqangi, ukwehlulela akusikhona kwamuntu ngaphandle kokuthi kungokukaMvelinqangi ngethembele kuyena futhi ikuyena lapho bethembela khona abanethemba”"